channel.title: What can I use to get my server online?
channel.description:
Hello... :) I want to have no-ip, but my dad doesn't want me to have other players on my computer. I have to fill in a password that only my dad knows. So I can't get no-ip and I don't want Hamachi. Is there a way to solve this problem? Please help me. Thanks for reading. ;)
- 0wnz0r

item.title: What can I use to get my server online?
item.dc:creator: @Luvodicus Luvodicus
item.description:
@Luvodicus wrote:

[quote=“Hcspure, post:4, topic:178751”]Use your direct IP?

www.ipchicken.com ?[/quote]

uh… no… yer an idiot, and that defeats the purpose of him posting in the first place…

Look, NO-IP doesnt give direct access to your computer… it gives access to the port that you’ve chosen to use, and in this case, it would be the port that your private server is running off of…

item.dc:creator: @Teutobod Teutobod
item.description:
@Teutobod wrote:

I want to have no-ip, but my dad doesn’t want me to have other players on my computer.

They’re not on your computer
When you open a server they can only play on it,they cant do or see anything on your computer.
Your server will save a .java file witch contains infos from the other players skill,items,coords,etc.Nothin more.
& your server ll do it if u have no-ip,hamachi or anything…
Sorry if i didnt understand somethin,srry for my english,i dont speak it very vell :S
